  "detailed_description": "<h1>Sincere Reminder</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dear valued customer, perfume is an intensely personal experience. What one person finds captivating, another may find intolerable. We sincerely ask that you take great care in making your purchase. Thank you so much for your understanding!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DREAMSTAIRS is a long-term experimental electronic perfume project that focuses on various sensations or moments. The entire series follows several general principles:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No settings. No saves. No pause.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Does not include any extreme horror elements or monsters.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>There will always be three or six perfumes in preview status.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>New single perfumes will be released in sequence according to the preview order. However, if a certain moment during a period is particularly captivating, there may be surprise releases.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>To prevent the game package from becoming too large, all subsequent perfumes, except for the first series, will be released as individual free DLCs alongside development.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>As people's understanding of the game evolves, the essence of the game will slowly transform, just like stairs, just like steps.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>JUNIOR.K  15.01.2025</strong></p></p><br><h1>New Collection Coming in 2025/26</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>New Collection Coming in 2025/2026</u>: <i>About time...</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336990/extras/2595748158834287961a017357a28640.avif?t=1736871217\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336990/extras_big/2595748158834287961a017357a28640.avif?t=1736871217 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Joker</strong> — You will spend the last day of some clowns' lives in a nursing home with them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Y2K</strong> — A quiet day indoors during the turn of the millennium, with a beautiful fish tank in the basement.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Just Yesterday</strong> — A classic 5v5 FPS match, with maps that you could recite with your eyes closed, and most importantly, your teammates are also comrades. But soon, you'll realize that something feels off about this game—it neither succeeded nor failed...</p></p><br><h1>2027/2028</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Speed=Humidity ≥ 0</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336990/extras/03bf835fafc5558dcee0d19f147b01d0.avif?t=1736871217\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336990/extras_big/03bf835fafc5558dcee0d19f147b01d0.avif?t=1736871217 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336990/extras/4dbf21bbd8444b1b6821ba6358d532c5.avif?t=1736871217\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336990/extras_big/4dbf21bbd8444b1b6821ba6358d532c5.avif?t=1736871217 width=800 height=450 /></span><strong>Dear Valued Customer,</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First and foremost, we sincerely hope you have a warm and enjoyable shopping experience. Before making your decision, we kindly remind you: <strong><i>if you think of this as a game, please do not purchase it!</i></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, if you are open to embracing it as <strong><u>your first electronic perfume</u></strong> and enjoy the enchanting atmosphere it brings when you spray it and take a stroll, <strong><i>we would be thrilled with your choice!</i></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This electronic perfume set features three distinct fragrances, inspired by a harmonious blend of ambient sound effects and the soothing echoes of footsteps, reminiscent of countless steps taken. The fragrances are labeled as <strong>MONTAGE, PleaseTravelersSafe&sounD, and CANDY</strong>,and come with a complimentary <strong>sample</strong>.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lastly,let us ponder once more that captivating question: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong><u>Do people dream of stairs?</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336990/extras/a5907d4bd8d2d8f997405d5e14761a25.avif?t=1736871217\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336990/extras_big/a5907d4bd8d2d8f997405d5e14761a25.avif?t=1736871217 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336990/extras/dbc4aced07b263b60e215272710e6e8c.avif?t=1736871217\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336990/extras_big/dbc4aced07b263b60e215272710e6e8c.avif?t=1736871217 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336990/extras/a146d67f340018332a0b0208148afb44.avif?t=1736871217\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336990/extras_big/a146d67f340018332a0b0208148afb44.avif?t=1736871217 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336990/extras/62f3da0919c40e9a5c328f72108fa08e.avif?t=1736871217\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336990/extras_big/62f3da0919c40e9a5c328f72108fa08e.avif?t=1736871217 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
